ents is\nobtained between the exact result and the result using effective field\ntheories.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 May 2006 17:18:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Sep 2006 12:48:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
